data.description: Fantastic home for entertaining and fitting any family style! Main floor has fabulous layout with: Vaulted ceilings, fireplace, kitchen with beautiful white cabinets, hardwood floors, and stunning tiled back splash, the laundry room, a bedroom, and bathroom, an office/den and overlooking backyard. Walkout to heated screened-in porch with deck! Upper floor has overlooking loft and two wings. The first has the primary bedroom with walk-in closet, ensuite and a  sliding French door office/den. The other wing has 2 bedrooms with plenty of closet room, a bathroom and 2 skylights for unique architectural design. Lower level has wet bar, recessed lighting, bathroom, storage room, and 2 additional bonus rooms for your hobbies! Recent landscaping on sprawling yard with an 8x12 shed and storage/workbench in garage. Close to parks, lakes, restaurants, theatre all while located on a cul-de-sac makes this your perfect home!!
